Package com.cafean.jobstream.server.components

Class Stream

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.jobstream.server.components.Stream
  • public class Stream
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing the top-level description of a complete job stream. This class and its contained objects include all of the properties and structures required to execute an entire stream.

    Objects of this type are created when reading a stream definition XML file and are used by every part of the server side of the job stream system.

    See Also:
    StreamDefinitionReader, Task, ApplicationDefinition, PlatformProperties
